

	 
      in pardeye nefrat angiz. har rooz ke miram az khoone biroon,hame ja hast.pardehaye rangarang,in hame pooshanande,ta zaat e har kas penhan shavad.ta zeshti kheili ha pooshide bemanad.yeki az doostam goft baraye inke az share soosk rahat she,az farsh estefade mikone. man az har pardeii motenaferam.az pardehaye otagham.az pardehaye mardom.hata az pardeii ke rooye morde myndazan. man az mardhaye zan zalili ke adaye gholdorha ro jeloye zanhaye dige dar myaran,va bezoor mikhan began zanha hichi nistan,ta naghse khodeshoon ro bepooshoonan ham bizaram.man az pardeye tahghire oonha ham bizaram. man az hameye oonhaii ke mikhan ba tahghire digaran khodeshoon o mohem jelve bedan ham badam myad. va az inke in hame nefrat dar man jaam shode ham badam myad.are miram kami gerye konam.gerye hameye nefrat ha ro mishoore.kesi ke hanooz mitoone gerye kone,mitoone omidvar bashe ke az ensanyat kharej nashode. pas bikhod nakhand o nago,"he he.gerye chie mage man bacham ke gerye konam?" kesi ke inhame zeshti bebine vo gerye nakone,ensan nist.oh,shayad ham nemibine.pas koore. va mozoo be hamin sadegye.    
    
